description:
Extract the standard context header block found at the top of all prompts.

## Source Pattern (common across all prompts)
```markdown
Read context from: ${CTX}
Progress file: ${PROGRESS}
Iteration: ${ITERATION}
```

## Variations
Some prompts include additional lines like:
- Status output: ${STATUS}
- Output file: ${OUTPUT_PATH}

## Target
scripts/lib/templates/fragments/context-header.md

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Template file created with common header
- [ ] Variables are passed through (resolved after include expansion)

